title: Awesome Value, Great Location
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHM/NJQQ', 'Huntington Park Apartments offers spacious studio, 1-, 2- and 3-bedroom apartment homes.', 'Enjoy private patios and balconies, the landscaped courtyard, community room, and the picnic and grilling areas.', 'We have controlled entries, professional on-site management and maintenance.', 'Fiber-optic internet service is available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Huntington Park home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Walk-in closet', 'Ceiling fan', 'Air conditioning', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Laundry facility', 'BBQ & picnic area', 'Bike storage', 'Fitness center', 'Package receiving', 'Playground', 'Huntington Park Apartments Information', 'Address:', '1245 Shakopee Ave E, Shakopee MN, 55379', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=13', 'Deposit:', "$500 (Note: Up to One Month's Rent Based on Credit & Income)", 'Application Fee:', '$45 (Note: Per Person)', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 - 200 (Note: Non-Refundable)', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '10:00AM - 4:00PM', 'Sunday:', '12:00PM - 4:00PM']
